

creat a github repository
Install the dependencies - requirement.txt
create .env and add configurable paths
create the docs_dir folder - for the documents
create the src folder (This contains all the source code)
create  folders inside the src (agents, backend, frontend, rag_doc_ingestion)
create __init__.py file inside the folders
In the gitignore folder, uncomment .idea
Add the vector db to the git ignore

Next
Document Ingestion
1. RAG document ingestion
- Create a config folder inside the rag-doc-ingestion
- Create a new file inside the 'config' folder - doc_ingestion_settings
- add the documents ingestion settings on the file
- Add another file 'ingest_doc' inside the 'rag_doc_ingestion' directory
- ingest_doc = will have the code to build your vector database
- Run this script --- python -m src.rag_doc_ingestion.ingest_docs

push to github
git add .
git status


